<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="13Jul1932"><font color="red">13 July 1932</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to T.S. Eliot): What am I to do about my book? Of course I can always refund the advance if I have to abandon it. But I want to finish it. Impossible to write in such circumstances &hellip; I really do not know what to do about <i>W.i.P.</i> </div>
